Add retry logic to axios client

File: frontend/src/shared/lib/api/client.ts

Add after apiClient creation:
```typescript
import axiosRetry from 'axios-retry'

axiosRetry(apiClient, {
  retries: 3,
  retryDelay: (retryCount) => {
    const delay = axiosRetry.exponentialDelay(retryCount)
    logger.info(`API retry attempt ${retryCount}, delay: ${delay}ms`)
    return delay
  },
  retryCondition: (error) => {
    return axiosRetry.isNetworkOrIdempotentRequestError(error)
  },
  onRetry: (retryCount, error, requestConfig) => {
    logger.warn(`API retry ${retryCount} for ${requestConfig.url}:`, error.message)
  },
})
```

Why this config:
- 3 retries max
- Exponential backoff (1s, 2s, 4s)
- Only for GET/PUT/DELETE (idempotent)
- NOT for POST/PATCH (non-idempotent)

